Package gov.lbl.glamm.server.dao.impl

Class Summary
AnnotatedMapDescriptorDAOImpl Implementation of AnnotatedMapDescriptorDAO interface.
CitationsGlammDAOImpl Implementations of the CitationsDAO interface.
CompoundGlammDAOImpl Implementation of the Compound DAO interface.
ExperimentDAOImpl Implementation of the Experiment DAO interface.
ExperimentMicroarrayDAOImpl Implementation of the Experiment DAO interface allowing access to the microarray data on MicrobesOnline.
ExperimentSessionDAOImpl Implementatin of the Experiment DAO interface allowing access to user-uploaded experiments.
GeneDAOImpl Implementation of the Gene DAO interface aggregating access to genes stored in MicrobesOnline, MetaMicrobesOnline, and user-uploaded genes stored per-session.
GeneMetaMolDAOImpl Implementation of the Gene DAO interface allowing access to genes stored in MetaMicrobesOnline.
GeneMolDAOImpl Implementation of the Gene DAO interface allowing access to genes in MicrobesOnline
GeneSessionDAOImpl Implementation of the Gene DAO for accessing user-uploaded gene data.
KeggPathwayDAOImpl Implementation of the Pathway DAO allowing access to KEGG pathways stored in the GLAMM database.
OrganismDAOImpl Implementation of the Organism DAO aggregating access to organisms stored in MetaMicrobesOnline, MicrobesOnline, as well as user-uploaded organisms stored per-session.
OrganismMetaMolDAOImpl Implementation of the Organism DAO interface granting access to organisms stored in MetaMicrobesOnline.
OrganismMolDAOImpl Implementation of the Organism DAO interface granting access to organisms stored in MicrobesOnline.
OrganismSessionDAOImpl Implementation of the Organism DAO interface granting access to user-uploaded organisms stored per-session.
ReactionGlammDAOImpl Implementation of the Reaction DAO interface granting access to reactions stored in the GLAMM database.
UserDAOImpl Implementation of the User DAO interface granting access to users stored in MicrobesOnline.
